text: Tom Haynes (born 9 September 1997) is an English cricketer. He made his first- class debut on 26 March 2019, for Loughborough MCCU against Leicestershire, as part of the Marylebone Cricket Club University fixtures. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:English cricketers Category:Loughborough MCCU cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
